All Things Git: The podcast about Git
=====================================

This is [www.allthingsgit.com](https://www.allthingsgit.com), the web site
for [All Things Git](https://www.allthingsgit.com), the podcast about Git.

[Edward Thomson](https://www.edwardthomson.com) and
[Martin Woodward](http://www.woodwardweb.com) talk to the people who build
Git, who create tools for it and who teach people how to use it. They
bring you a new episode every two weeks, discussing the Git version
control system with a guest. Subscribe to the podcast on our 
[RSS](https://www.allthingsgit.com/rss.xml).

And be sure to follow us on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/allthingsgit)
and [Facebook](https://facebook.com/allthingsgit).
